sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant CDN
    participant Gateway
    participant AuthService
    participant RateLimiter
    participant Router
    participant ServiceA
    participant ServiceB
    participant ServiceC
    participant Cache
    participant Database
    participant Queue
    participant Logger
    Client->>CDN: Request
    CDN->>Gateway: Cache miss
    Gateway->>AuthService: Validate token
    AuthService-->>Gateway: OK
    Gateway->>RateLimiter: Check quota
    RateLimiter-->>Gateway: Allowed
    Gateway->>Router: Route request
    Router->>ServiceA: Handle
    ServiceA->>ServiceB: Fetch data
    ServiceB->>Cache: Lookup
    Cache-->>ServiceB: Miss
    ServiceB->>Database: Query
    Database-->>ServiceB: Results
    ServiceB->>Cache: Populate
    ServiceB-->>ServiceA: Data
    ServiceA->>ServiceC: Enrich
    ServiceC-->>ServiceA: Enriched
    ServiceA->>Queue: Emit event
    ServiceA->>Logger: Audit log
    ServiceA-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>CDN: Response
    CDN-->>Client: Response
